"support power off.<br /><br />Click \"Proceed\" below to power off your "
"device."
msgstr ""

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:154
msgid "Waiting for device..."
msgstr "डिवाइस की प्रतीक्षा…"

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:391
msgid ""
"Warning: Device (%s) is unknown or isn't a dual-firmware device!%sIf you are "
"seeing this on an OpenWrt dual-firmware supported device,%splease refer to "
"%sHow to add a new device section of the README%s."
msgstr ""
"चेतावनी: डिवाइस (%s) अज्ञात है या यह दोहरी-फर्मवेयर डिवाइस नहीं है! %sयदि आप इसे "
"OpenWrt दोहरी-फर्मवेयर समर्थित डिवाइस पर देख रहे हैं, तो कृपया README%s के %sनया "
"डिवाइस कैसे जोड़ें अनुभाग देखें।"

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:376
msgid "Warning: There are unsaved changes that will get lost on reboot!"
msgstr "चेतावनी: कुछ परिवर्तन सहेजे नहीं गए हैं जो रीबूट करने पर नष्ट हो जाएंगे!"

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:481
msgid "Warning: This system does not support powering off!"
msgstr "चेतावनी: यह सिस्टम पावर बंद करने का समर्थन नहीं करता है!"

#: applications/luci-app-advanced-reboot/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/system/advanced-reboot.js:462
